data.description: Lovely 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home featuring a private backyard locating in a quiet and established community. This home features a bright family room with towering widows and ceilings, am eat-in kitchen including large island and wood cabinets, a flexible space that lends way to a perfect office or hobby area, and a backyard that includes a large screened in patio and additional deck overlooking tranquil woods and a pond where there are regular deer sightings. You will also find three spacious bedrooms including a primary suite boasting a walk-in closet and ensuite. You will also be pleased to find a recently replaced roof (December 2023) and new carpet (June 2023) and newer HVAC system. This home has easy access to to restaurants, shops, etc. while allowing you to enjoy a quite haven. You will find that this is the ultimate space to unwind.
